<L>__{exterior black cove farm. night}
<A>__{it's pouting with rain. inside the farmhouse, ada is playing}
<B>__{the piano.}
<A>__{men and women crowd into the parlour, in best clothes, celebrating the completion of the chapel. inman is outside on the porch, his coat soaked, water pouring off his hat. he looks at ada. she finishes. monroe steps in front of the applause, smiling. his words of thanks leak through the window to inman, who stands, watching, listening.}
